.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: apricot, banana, blueberry, cranberry, pumpkin, radish, strawberry
There are 7 different favourite colors: black, apricot, ivory, blood-red, brown, lilac, emerald
There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the french is the person who likes blood-red##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the mexican is the person who likes black##1
10. the american is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person who likes ivory is the turkish##1
12. the person eating banana is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes ivory and the person who likes blood-red##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Food          | banana  | radish    | pumpkin  | apricot | cranberry  | strawberry | blueberry |
| Color   | brown | ivory | emerald   | blood-red   | lilac | black     | apricot |
