 3. the freelancer is the chinese##1
 4. the firefighter is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the australian is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is the doctor##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is the australian##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the colombian is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the person who's hobby is camping is the indian##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the australian##1
16. the person who's hobby is video-games is the french##1

