7 different games are played: bridge, billiard, canasta, monopoly, whist, chess, poker
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, skateboard, taxi, train, tram
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the person eating radish is between the person eating cherry and the person eating grapes##2
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is the person playing poker##1
 7. the person eating cherry is the person driving the train##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person playing chess##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the person playing monopoly##1
15. the person eating radish is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
